Create a Mavan project in eclipse (ex : Automation Project 1) 
Add the related dependencies jar files (selenium, java, jnit, cucumber and cucumber java) in pom.html file by entering the group ID and artifact ID.
Create the package under the project under src/ test/ resources
Create the feature files under 'src/ test/ resources' folder. (Refer : feature files uploaded)
Create the steps file (java class) under 'src/test/java' folder. (Refer : Steps files uploaded)
Create the runner class to setup the framework under src/test/ java (Refer : Runner.class)
Run the runner file / package for output verification.
